Credit Lyonnais is issuing a 19 billionyen zero coupon eurobond due April 15, 1992 priced at 81.22pct, lead manager Nomura International Ltd said.    The bond is available in denominations of 10 mln yen andwill be listed in Luxembourg.    Credit Lyonnais is joint lead. Fees comprise 85 basispoints selling concession and 70 basis points for managementand underwriting.    Payment date is April 15. REUTER&#3;